node.text:
How do you show up for yourself? 
Life is busy and it’s so easy to get caught up in your to-do list, then poof, the week is gone. When I get overwhelmed over the past year with all that’s on my plate, I’ve learned to let go of my perfectionistic expectations. I’ve let go of the idea that it all has to be done. We are not measured by how much we get checked off our list, so much can wait till tomorrow. 
I show up for myself by spending time reading with my cup of coffee to start my day , taking a hot bath while I listen to some great music, and sometimes by catching lunch with a friend that inspires me. ( Let’s not forget catching up on a superhero movie 😂) When life moves in a slower motion, we have time to connect to ourselves and our purpose. Life is the sweetest gift we’ve been given..... don’t waste a minute of it.

This is our first family day with Oakley, and I got to say it’s so more fun with her. We will be packing our day full of playing toys, chasing her around the house and eating the rest of our valentines chocolates. It’s snowing like crazy here and we are getting over a cough so no outside activities for us.  For those who are not in Alberta today is a long weekend for us, but for you it’s just a Monday. Well happy Monday and stay tune this week we are part of a giveaway I’m dying to have.

node.text:
There is a great magic about the ocean, the beauty of it. It’s like we all are drawn to it. Sadly, even what we wear may have a negative impact to it. Did you know that synthetic fibers are polluting our environment just by being washed in a washing machine? Hundreds of thousands of fibers can be released after every washing and reach ground water and oceans – a supply, that is vital for all living beings. If you care about your surroundings and yourself, we encourage to take a small step and join us on synthetics free future by choosing natural fibers, like our beloved linen. By wisely choosing what you wear, you can contribute to wellness of our flora and fauna.

Сменяются времена года и правители. 
Вышитые брошки разлетаются по континентам. 
Шьются и находят своих владелиц платья. 
Все платья, кроме этого красного.
🤷‍♀️🤷‍♀️🤷‍♀️

Колдовство, не иначе
🧙‍♀️🧙‍♀️🧙‍♀️
✨💫⚡️

На груди небольшой кармашек, и два удобных вместительных кармана в боковых швах юбки. 
Сама юбка достаточной ширины, складок ни много, ни мало, а столько, сколько нужно👌 
Платье можно носить свободным или приталить, затянув шнурок на поясе. 
42 размер
На фото я, 170см роста.
100% лён средней плотности
7200р.

node.text:
In questi giorni, sul mio banco nel lab, sono circondata da diversi colori. Dal verde al giallo senape passando per il rosa fino al beige. Fra tutti però spicca il bianco! 
Non mi meraviglia che lo stiate scegliendo: le cerimonie dei prossimi mesi richiedono spesso l'uso di questo colore.
Io lo amo particolarmente! Mi parla di luce, di purezza e semplicità. 🌿
L'abbinata lino-merletto vi è piaciuta tanto. Devo dire che il pizzo dona al lino un tocco di leggerezza in più. E per questo lo rivedrete presto.
🌿
Mi preparo a un weekend freddo ma con il sole. Prevedo una passeggiata, tempo da passare in famiglia e serenità. Il tuo weekend invece??
.
